data.description: MOVE IN READY! Check out this gorgeous brick front home in this highly sought after Broadstone community. Amazing location across the street from the clubhouse which includes a playground and tennis court! This beautiful floorplan includes a Bedroom on the Main level that is large enough to be considered a second master! The oversized upstairs master bedroom has its own sitting area, huge walk in closet, spacious bathroom with separate tub and shower with a double vanity sink. Brand new vanities with marble countertops in bathroom. Brand new  Gorgeous entry foyer has tall ceilings and wide hallways! Formal living room and separate dining room. The spacious kitchen looks out to the large family room to include a fireplace.  The bright kitchen includes white cabinets, granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances and an eat in kitchen. All of the bedrooms get tons of natural lights and have large closets. The huge fenced backyard is perfect for entertaining. 5k ADT camera security system included in the sale. Brand new HVAC w/ 10 year warranty included in price. Brand new paint, fixtures, LVT flooring and carpet.  One of the largest floor plans in the complex! Don't miss out on this beautiful home!    *** THIS HOME QUALIFIES FOR 100% FINANCING WITH AN 8K GRANT! ASK ME HOW TO GET QUALIFIED! ****
